    "In this section, we compare two common approaches to layer-wise pruning, namely iterative layer pruning and middle-layer pruning.",
    "Moreover, we compare using chrF/chrF++ and COMET for layer importance evaluation during iterative layer pruning.",
    "In all cases, we only work on decoder layers (cf.",
    "Section 4.2)."
